{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-part-intro-template-js","path":"/zh/part3","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<div class=\"intro\">\n<!-- In this part our focus shifts towards the backend, that is, towards implementing functionality on the server side of the stack. We will implement a simple REST API in Node.js by using the Express library, and the application's data will be stored in a MongoDB database. At the end of this part, we will deploy our application to the internet.-->\n<p>在这一部分，我们将重点转向后端，也就是在全栈中的服务端实现功能。我们将用 Express 库在 Node.js 中实现一个简单的 REST API，并将应用的数据将存储在 MongoDB 数据库中。在这一章节的最后，我们将把我们的应用部署到互联网上。</p>\n<!-- <i>Part updated on 16th March 2025</i> -->\n<p><i>原文更新于 2025 年 3 月 16 日<i></p>\n<!-- - <i>Node updated to version v22.3.0</i> -->\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><i>Node 版本更新至 v22.3.0</i></p>\n<!-- - <i>Nodemon replaced with the node --watch command</i> -->\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><i>nodemon 替换为 node --watch 命令</i></p>\n<!-- - <i>MongoDB instructions updated and reformatted</i> -->\n</li>\n<li><i>更新并格式化 MongoDB 指令</i></li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"mainImage":{"publicURL":"/static/8ac7bc0fb2b7018a7853b00c454b2103/part-3.svg"},"part":3,"lang":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"part":3,"lang":"zh"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518"]}